{"tid":1979980,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"西貢藍店 爽一爽","createTime":"2020-04-19T20:35:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-24T16:35:50.000Z","uid":185670,"like":111,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":47,"replies":[{"pid":"abc0dff0e9482ef497776893cb060d97ba6134c0","tid":1979980,"uid":185670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T20:35:30.000Z","msg":"呢排分化問題嚴重<br />\n好希望大家可以睇下我下面講嘅嘢<br />\n<br />\n前排因為爆發支那武漢肺炎，大家都少左出街啦<br />\n無酒吧？無戲院？無美容院？<br />\n無問題！無嘢可以阻到香港人出街！<br />\n因為好撚多人決定去行山，而西貢正正就係行山、露營同出海玩嘅熱點<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">重點係</span></span><br />\n我係一個西貢人，住左係西貢二十幾年，<br />\n有條食街好出名，都有唔少黃店。<br />\n不過有一間仆街嘅鋪頭叫<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">爽一爽</span></span><br />\n之前未有貢茶同阿四糖水之前，就只有佢一間，所以大家都冇得選擇。<br />\n但自從多左兩間選擇之後，再因為佢對面嘅阿四糖水係黃店，所以佢生意差左就一定嘅。<br />\n係疫情之下，佢地就係知大家入嚟玩，都會去揾黃店嚟食/打卡宣傳，佢地就食住個勢嚟<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">扮黃賺錢</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n上年運動開始左一段時間嘅時候，我同朋友仲有去爽一爽買嘢飲，點知未行到門口，就已經聽到佢同對面&lsquo;餃餃震&rsquo;個老細一齊好大聲咁屌鳩示威者搞事。<br />\n<br />\n我都問過身邊嘅朋友，原來都有好幾位聽過爽一爽老細講過類似嘅說話。<br />\n西貢咁細，要知道佢地係黃係藍又有幾難？<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rY0pNCg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrY0pNCg.jpg&h=87e93b2d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n張單打句「醫護」，「光榮」就代表你係黃？<br />\n你有冇捐過錢？有冇罷過工？<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">冇！你連一張文宣都冇呀</span></span><br />\n我地西貢街坊一直都有update黃店同藍店上和你eat，但可能因為太多投稿，所以爽一爽就一直無回應。<br />\n大家都明白之前對黃店嘅門檻太高，依家呢個情況好左好多<br />\n但你依家係擺撚到明係<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">深藍扮黃</span></span>呀<br />\n憑咩要俾錢呢啲仆街賺錢？我攞去捐俾手足/買物資唔好呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MMnGPSw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMMnGPSw.jpg&h=331212af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n係鋪頭個facebook講休息，<br />\n當有人問:去旅行嗎？<br />\nKi Siu Yin :女兒放暑假，去玩幾日<br />\n咁樣覆得嘅，點睇都係老細啦下嘛？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咦？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">話說老細你去完旅行有冇隔離十四日呀？</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nKi Siu Yin facebook <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">疑似爽一爽老細私人fb</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v80pNFw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv80pNFw.jpg&h=7b0cc389&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GQAM00G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGQAM00G.jpg&h=76562174&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n爽一爽鋪面(呢張都幾年前架啦)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fbbgDS4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfbbgDS4.png&h=521ce18e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我預左會有人屌鳩我係分化撚<br />\n但係人地賺我地錢賺到笑啦，香港人可唔可以醒目少少呀？<br />\n每個人都要有<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">獨立思考</span></strong></span>，唔好人地講幾句就信啦！"},{"pid":"99337c0e0bb908872898aea511896d45058d42af","tid":1979980,"uid":163167,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T20:37:17.000Z","msg":"藍黃同鬥黃唔同<br />\n係良知嘅分別<br />\n要分清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aed2309618674e1aefc762ffb1b81871a0499df4","tid":1979980,"uid":185670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T20:38:04.000Z","msg":"大家幫手推同埋share俾身邊嘅人知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6cafd4542453f76bab868ed54d53edd8845d7c7","tid":1979980,"uid":185670,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T20:39:39.000Z","msg":"推到佢仆街呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/norma