0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0d1c64674ad93833c0c1ada6af132e6ae16b66c3","tid":1979980,"uid":79566,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T20:42:57.000Z","msg":"一早知佢係藍已經好耐冇飲<br />\n先唔講政治，以前佢岩岩開10蚊杯珍珠奶茶係幾抵，個陣仲覺得佢地兩公婆都幾有人情味會嗲兩句，點知佢愈做愈大，又搞雞蛋仔又做淘寶攞貨個啲，兩公婆壓力大左之後就冇咁親民，個光頭佬又黑面，啲野飲都冇以前咁好飲。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T20:45:56.000Z","msg":"前排個朋友先send左張相俾我睇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ujXcchT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FujXcchT.png&h=8d0560ae&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f5a4f8e3e08f8712e5b0e4c660031b3a103c0f99","tid":1979980,"uid":185670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c025f6a7bd2aa584eeefc95521c8295b927d875d","tid":1979980,"uid":46400,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"bf1f4bc31d765d5f7a5c56e935ad9dc3fb441892","tid":1979980,"uid":185670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"99337c0e0bb908872898aea511896d45058d42af","tid":1979980,"uid":163167,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T20:37:17.000Z","msg":"藍黃同鬥黃唔同<br />\n係良知嘅分別<br />\n要分清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T20:41:25.000Z","msg":"知佢係偽黃賺錢<br />\n更加無必要俾面佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T20:44:33.000Z","msg":"佢意思咪話呢間係真藍扮黃店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />可以批鬥囉<br />\n夠唔夠黃果啲就唔好再講"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T20:47:07.000Z","msg":"我明啊巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b28e7c3620ff48ed4c171fed751c87d0cabe3dbb","tid":1979980,"uid":185670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T20:48:35.000Z","msg":"推到佢仆街呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dca25450b18b8b979b9f642bbde5659f992c8d3b","tid":1979980,"uid":44260,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T20:58:23.000Z","msg":"佢兩公婆串到呢，成日叫人唔等得就唔好買，得個女面口好啲"},{"pid":"9b48c4019ec95756463117c48b9a3f4bb4330369","tid":1979980,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T21:05:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e04d79feb797f2133af64877b1e2b345fb755465","tid":1979980,"uid":209773,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T21:10:10.000Z","msg":"黃佢老味咩呢間，你話貼文宣罷過工，就算個老細俾人起底揾到佢以前係藍絲都有得傾。<br />\n而家淨係得後面嗰part，冇前面嗰part<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50a39647e9074a018903b0ff480864ea9cfbe400","tid":1979980,"uid":294121,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T21:16:37.000Z","msg":"未反送中前幫襯過一次<br />\n態度差又西面<br />\n叫完杯野唔俾飛<br />\n問佢拎又扮聽唔到<br />\n叫到我杯野個名同佢講頭先無俾飛又係十問九唔應<br />\n之後淨係去阿四買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又有後生靚女睇<br />\n唔使對住個黑口黑面麻甩佬<br />\n不過好多鬼仔鬼妹去買<br />\n同堆餃餃震都係藍？"},{"pid":"b1943a5f203c7b89cf3f8ac4f372304c2ac6d42e","tid":1979980,"uid":185670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"50a39647e9074a018903b0ff480864ea9cfbe400","tid":1979980,"uid":294121,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T21:16:37.000Z","msg":"未反送中前幫襯過一次<br />\n態度差又西面<br />\n叫完杯野唔俾飛<br />\n問佢拎又扮聽唔到<br />\n叫到我杯野個名同佢講頭先無俾飛又係十問九唔應<br />\n之後淨係去阿四買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又有後生靚女睇<br />\n唔使對住個黑口黑面麻甩佬<br />\n不過好多鬼仔鬼妹去買<br />\n同堆餃餃震都係藍？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T21:33:53.000Z","msg":"爽一爽個光頭佬真係睇到都唔開胃<br />\n餃餃震都係藍架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b733fbdc1c80642c1413716277dab97f8bd3c62a","tid":1979980,"uid":46142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T02:09:05.000Z","msg":"幫你推下"},{"pid":"99851565814e66759917b8de459320e9625fc6ac","tid":1979980,"uid":68115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T02:29:13.000Z","msg":"我住左西貢廿幾年 一次都無飲過"},{"pid":"769bd6a18406a0ce8531aff8c7ecca3f6f2cb48b","tid":1979980,"uid":288478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T02:31:39.000Z","msg":"餃餃震都係藍？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3924dcec8345389a9891a14d6167206ea967d3ea","tid":1979980,"uid":44031,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T02:35:29.000Z","msg":"住西貢 <br />\n佢地不嬲都難飲到閪咁 兩公婆啲善良扮出黎架姐<br />\n年幾前 佢地租埋隔離個舖位 想發大黎搞 <br />\n結果搞唔撚掂 日日閪哂口面<br />\n自從啊四出現左 佢就含撚啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人地又好飲 又有妹妹睇 又係黃店 <br />\n冇競爭以為自己好撚掂"},{"pid":"a52b0e8e7519677dd70fb0112bcdbf69a917fe3a","tid":1979980,"uid":232817,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T02:37:50.000Z","msg":"依啲要推啦，得閒鬥黃不如搵依啲出黎仲好，依啲唔係偽黃，直頭係藍扮黃"},{"pid":"6485e30f441e100dba4785a40ad3a0033ca55e6d","tid":1979980,"uid":91317,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T02:41:14.000Z","msg":"嘩屌成日食佢D格仔餅添, 因為成個西貢得佢有好似"},{"pid":"2d7b558683727ea931414a1bd455f765e63d9920","tid":1979980,"uid":108016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T02:41:53.000Z","msg":"有冇 tg group?<br />\n放上 tg group 啦"},{"pid":"b29e70b812e984684cdd6a383dd70d5b3943a3a2","tid":1979980,"uid":61235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T02:42:41.000Z","msg":"你SEND去 和你EAT 黃藍商戶 呢D好過啦<br />\n個個都SEND晒等佢FC 決定改唔改<br />\n講真,大部分人跟APP搵黃店<br />\n你呢D POST過幾日就沉啦<br />\n再者唔住開西貢都唔會記得"},{"pid":"bf18c128509a22edfd16c3825dd83128d2e54a57","tid":1979980,"uid":209188,"like":1,"disli